videos.description: Marshall RB Tyler King is hit in the backfield and fumbles giving Cincinnati great field position in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Marshall coughs it up on first drive

videos.description: Cincinnati QB Hayden Moore looses his grip trying to pump fake and throws a backwards screen pass as Marshall jumps on the live ball.
videos.headline: Thundering Herd capitalize on botched screen

videos.description: Marshall QB Chase Litton fools the Cincinnati defense with a play action fake and throws to an open Ryan Yuracheck for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Litton lobs TD pass to Yuracheck over the middle

videos.description: Marshall QB Chase Litton extends the Thundering Herd's lead before halftime with a 27-yard touchdown throw to Willie Johnson to bring Marshall up 17-0.
videos.headline: Litton rolls left and throws TD

videos.description: The Thundering Herd force a Bearcats fumble on the kickoff and score on the next play as Ryan Yurachek fights to the goal line for his second score of the game.
videos.headline: Back-to-back scores for Marshall

videos.description: Cincinnati's offensive line open a huge hole for Michael Warren II who runs 27 yards for an easy touchdown.
videos.headline: Warren runs untouched for TD

videos.description: On fourth down, Marshall RB Keion Davis scores from a yard out to give the Thundering Herd a 24-point fourth quarter lead.
videos.headline: Davis powers through goal line for TD

videos.description: A combination of timely turnovers and solid offensive line play propel the Thunder Herd to a statement win over Bearcats.
videos.headline: Marshall's offensive line controls Cincinnati's front seven in statement win
